  <summary date="2021-03-22T18:02:10Z" status="Introduced in House">Energy Resilient Communities Act 

This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a program that awards grants to make critical energy infrastructure more resilient to climate change hazards, such as grants for developing clean energy microgrids that support critical community infrastructure or customers of electric utilities with special energy needs due to medical conditions.</summary>
